\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e438b5b52bf2e8c32b96327ce02f9fb1b588ab52","tid":482869,"uid":110377,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T16:24:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>監察領展的團體，不滿領展將本地商場出售後，新業主管理不善，先後在股東大會及業績會中示威，要求領展停止出售商場。<br />\n<br />\n好矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 晒氣，班友都唔知自己想點</blockquote><br />\n有領展公關就笑言：「佢地做戲遮，笑住示威既，無事既，叫完口號就走架啦」"},{"pid":"708434d1b7c4f8d31f86e43ad5d516adb62f3367","tid":482869,"uid":95201,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T17:33:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收租佬都睇唔好後市，寧願套現</blockquote><br />\n呢17個商場只有4個做左AEI，其餘13個都冇做，即係代表管理層預期即使做左AEI都唔會令物業租金勁升，租金升唔到就等於物業價值唔升，咁呢d低增長既資產當然係趁市旺賣走佢，留多d錢去買具升值潛力既物業，或者減債or回購。<br />\n而回購既機會最大，因為租金收少左，要令DPU上升既方法一係就派多d，一係就回購減少股份數目。前者係無可能，因為出售物業所得既錢唔可以派，所以得番後者，而後者亦有利長遠每股派息增長。所以我覺得呢70幾億好大機會回購"},{"pid":"41138d9e1d457ed684ff0211422f0e05941916f2","tid":482869,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T17:34:09.000Z","msg":"改完名真正洗底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21c1731ef526995d83f0a8f2ad2ba318a61fd5b","tid":482869,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T23:11:47.000Z","msg":"HANDS都賣？"},{"pid":"f69ad0ae704a4a57d5e61e6fe12ee162445d14e7","tid":482869,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:55:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>改完名真正洗底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好領展"}]}